'''José Álvaro Pelegrín Gestido Pose''' (17 May 1907 &mdash; 18 January 1957) was a [[Association football|footballer]] from [[Uruguay]]. He was born in [[Montevideo]]. From 1926 to 1942, he played for [[C.A. Peñarol]]. He also played 25 matches for the [[Uruguay national football team]], winning the [[1930 FIFA World Cup]] and the [[1928 Summer Olympics]]. His brother [[Óscar Diego Gestido]] was President of Uruguay in 1967.

