{{unreferenced|date=March 2009}} '''Henri M. J. de Deken''' ([[Schoten]], 3 August 1907 – 12 February 1960) was a [[Belgium|Belgian]] [[football (soccer)]] player in defender role.
In career he played mostly for [[R. Antwerp F.C.|Royal Antwerp FC]]. For [[Belgium national football team]] he was in roster for [[1930 FIFA World Cup]], played one match with [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay]], losses 0&ndash;1.
