{{Spanish name 2|Rodríguez|González}} '''Raymundo Rodríguez González''' (15 April 1905 - date of death unknown), nicknamed ''Mapache''{{Ref|1}}, - was a [[Mexican people|Mexican]] [[football (soccer)|footballer]].
==Career== Rodríguez participated in the [[1930 FIFA World Cup]]. He played only in one game in the tournament, a match against [[Argentina national football team|Argentina]]{{Ref|2}}. During this period, his club was [[Marte FC]].
