== Career ==
During his career he has made twelve appearances and five goal for the Romanian national team. His career in club football was spent in [[NCS Salonta]] between 1924–1928, in [[CA Oradea]] in 1928-1937 and [[FC Ploieşti]] in 1948 <ref>[http://www.romaniansoccer.ro/players/k/kocsis_elemer.shtmll Stats on Romaniasoccer.ro]</ref>
