{{Infobox football biography | name = Constantin Stanciu | image = Constantin Stanciu.jpg | height = | birth_date = April 13, 1911 | birth_place = [[Bucharest]] | death_date = | position = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]] | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = | years1 = 1923-1927 | years2 = 1926-1927 | years3 = 1927-1935 | years4 = 1935-1939 | years5 = 1939 | clubs1 = [[Venus Bucureşti]] | clubs2 = [[Fulgerul Chişinău]] | clubs3 = [[Venus Bucureşti]] | clubs4 = [[FC Juventus Bucureşti (1924)|FC Juventus Bucureşti]] | clubs5 = [[Metalosport Bucureşti]] | caps1 = - | caps2 = - | caps3 = 62 | caps4 = 22 | caps5 = - | goals1 = - | goals2 = - | goals3 = 4 | goals4 = 2 | goals5 = - | nationalyears1 = 1929-1931 | nationalteam1 = [[Romania national football team|Romania]] | nationalcaps1 = 8 | nationalgoals1 = 4 | pcupdate = | ntupdate = }} '''Constantin Stanciu''' (April 13, 1911 in [[Bucharest]]) was a Romanian [[Association football|football]] [[Forward (association football)|forward]].
==Career== During his career he made eight appearances and scored four goals for the Romanian national team. His career in club football was spent at [[Venus Bucureşti]] between 1923–1927, he played for [[Fulgerul Chişinău]] in 1926-1927 and he returned to [[Venus Bucureşti]]. He then played for [[FC Petrolul Ploiești|Juventus Bucureşti]] until 1939, and he terminated his career in 1939 with Metalosport Bucureşti.<ref>[http://www.romaniansoccer.ro/players/s/stanciu_constantin.shtml Stats on Romaniasoccer.ro]</ref>
