{{Infobox football biography | image = | name = Eduardo Reyes Ortiz | height = | birth_date = {{Birth date|1907|1|1}} | birth_place = [[Bolivia]] | death_date = | position = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]] | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = | years1 = 1930 | clubs1 = [[The Strongest]] | caps1 = ? | goals1 = ? | nationalyears1 = 1930 | nationalteam1 = [[Bolivia national football team|Bolivia]] | nationalcaps1 = 1 | nationalgoals1 = 0 | pcupdate = | ntupdate = }} '''Eduardo Reyes Ortiz''' (born 1 January 1907 in [[Bolivia]]) was a [[Bolivia]]n [[Association football|football]] [[Forward (association football)|Forward]].
== Career ==
During his career he has made one appearances for the Bolivian national team at the [[1930 FIFA World Cup]]. He has passed his career in the club in [[The Strongest]].<ref>[http://www.worldfootball.net/spieler_profil/eduardo-reyes/ World Football Stats]</ref>
