'''Dragoslav „Dragan“ Mihajlović''' (13 December 1906 in [[Aleksinac]] &ndash; 18 June 1978) was a [[Yugoslavia|Yugoslav]] footballer. He played for the [[Yugoslavia national football team|Yugoslav national team]] at the [[1930 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>[http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/archive/edition=1/teams/team=43975.html]</ref> In 1944 he emigrated to [[Sale, Victoria|Sale]], [[Australia]].
