'''Bernabé Rivera Núñez'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://homepages.enterprise.net/eico/1930.htm |accessdate=June 14, 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/20120414231834/http://homepages.enterprise.net/eico/1930.htm |archivedate=April 14, 2012 }}</ref> was a [[Paraguay]]an [[association football|football]] [[Forward (association football)|forward]] who played for [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay]] in the [[1930 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>[http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/archive/edition=1/teams/team=43928.html 1930 FIFA World Cup Uruguay]</ref> He also played for [[Club Sportivo Luqueño]].
