{{Infobox football biography | image = | name = Miguel Brito | height = | birth_date = | birth_place = [[Bolivia]] | death_date = | position = [[Midfielder]] | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = | years1 = 1930 | clubs1 = [[Oruro Royal]] | caps1 = ? | goals1 = ? | nationalyears1 = 1930 | nationalteam1 = [[Bolivia national football team|Bolivia]] | nationalcaps1 = 0 | nationalgoals1 = 0 | pcupdate = | ntupdate = }} '''Miguel Brito''' was a [[Bolivia]]n [[Association football|football]] [[Midfielder]].
== Career ==
During his career he participated and made zero appearances for the Bolivian national team at the [[1930 FIFA World Cup]]. His career in club football was spent in Oruro Royal <ref>[http://www.worldfootball.net/spieler_profil/miguel-brito/ World Football stats]</ref>
