{{Infobox football biography | image = | name = Gumercindo Gómez | height = | birth_date = {{Birth date|df=yes|1907|1|21}} | birth_place = [[Bolivia]] | death_date = {{death date and age|df=yes|1980|1|31|1907|1|21}} | position = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]] | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = | years1 = | clubs1 = | caps1 = | goals1 = | nationalyears1 = 1930 | nationalteam1 = [[Bolivia national football team|Bolivia]] | nationalcaps1 = 1 | nationalgoals1 = 0 | pcupdate = | ntupdate = }} '''Gumercindo Gomez''' (1907–1980, in [[Bolivia]]) was a Bolivian [[Association football|football]] [[Forward (association football)|Forward]].
== Career ==
During his career he has made one appearance for the Bolivian national team at the [[1930 FIFA World Cup]]. His career in club football was spent in Oruro Royal between 1929 and 1931 <ref>[http://www.worldfootball.net/spieler_profil/gumercindo-gomez/ World Football stats]</ref>
