{{Infobox football biography |image = |name = Jesús Castro |fullname = Jesús Castro Aguirol |height = |birth_date = |birth_place = [[Mexico]] |death_date = |position = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]] |youthyears1 = |youthclubs1 = |years1 = c.1930 |clubs1 = [[Club América]] |caps1 = |goals1 = |nationalyears1 = 1930 |nationalteam1 = [[Mexico national football team|Mexico]] |nationalcaps1 = 0 |nationalgoals1 = 0 }} '''Jesús Castro Aguirol''' was a Mexican amateur [[Association football|football]]er who played as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]]. He played his club football for [[Club América]] and was an unused member of the [[Mexico national football team|Mexico]] squad for the [[1930 FIFA World Cup|1930 World Cup]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Jesus Castro profile |url=http://ita.worldfootball.net/spieler_profil/jesus-castro/ |publisher=worldfootball.net|accessdate=15 October 2011}}</ref>
